Cell["\<\
The actual way to represent the outcomes is not so important. Their frequency \
is important. \
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.780580842995413*^9, 3.780580873304283*^9}, {
  3.780581096280386*^9, 3.780581104023982*^9}, {3.8128701860716877`*^9, 
